{"tid":1517564,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"楊衛隆：收到風美國議員已停止為港發聲","createTime":"2019-08-30T03:09:04.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-30T07:15:11.000Z","uid":271434,"like":22,"dislike":303,"uniUserReply":88,"replies":[{"pid":"cc7ff7dda0e951e2e2445fae9e7032cccd35b13d","tid":1517564,"uid":271434,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-30T03:09:04.000Z","msg":"美國經濟專家楊衛隆：<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">香港人被販民出賣了</span></span><br />\n販民不是反送中運動大台，但是，販民在美國議員面前扮大台。<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">販民和建制跑去美國和美國國會議員開「閉門會議」表示建制和販民達成協議，示威者得到滿意回應，反送中運動和平結束。今天楊某收到美國吹來的風，建制販民在閉門會議向美國議員表示販民已經達到共識，反送中示威和平結束。</span></span><br />\n今日，黃之鋒和陳浩天被捕，岑子杰遇襲。林賤企圖以大規模拘捕行動瓦解示威組織，拘捕和打擊所有示威組織知名人士，包括申請示威的攪手讓反送中示威平靜下來。<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">美國人就會相信反送中示威完結，美國人可以收工。</span><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">看吧，這幾天，美國議員全部靜下來，沒有發表支持香港反送中言論。</span></span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">販民已經淪為港共政治工具，為港共效力，替林賤消愁解困。建制販民可能已經安排日後成立假自治政治，分豬肉式撈好處。香港人被販民出賣了。</span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/yeungwailung/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fyeungwailung%2F&d=Fe1Xron1KfJbBj576sEg8t%2FmPfBwacFXLzUp2rw9Z8Q%3D&h=9ac5b035\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/yeungwailung/</a>"},{"pid":"51d196ec1dd4972fb0cab2289196cb43f1dbfa4a","tid":1517564,"uid":123991,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-30T03:09:15.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Mhik2fq.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FMhik2fq.gif&h=7b54c7c9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n九月一號下午一點機場見<br />\n<br />\n901機場和你塞 Channel<br />\n<a href=\"http://t.me/stuckwithyou\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fstuckwithyou&d=Fe1Xron1KfJbBj576sEg8t%2FmPfBwacFXLzUp2rw9Z8Q%3D&h=a3868ff4\" target=\"_blank\">http://t.me/stuckwithyou</a><br />\n901機場