"font-size: x-large;\">販民已經淪為港共政治工具，為港共效力，替林賤消愁解困。建制販民可能已經安排日後成立假自治政治，分豬肉式撈好處。香港人被販民出賣了。</span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/yeungwailung/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fyeungwailung%2F&d=Fe1Xron1KfJbBj576sEg8t%2FmPfBwacFXLzUp2rw9Z8Q%3D&h=9ac5b035\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/yeungwailung/</a>"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-30T03:20:20.000Z","msg":"人地有領事館係度收風, 唔洗靠香港泛民"},{"pid":"fa0cb5b751b77abf486fafbc9e9d0b805ca569aa","tid":1517564,"uid":41343,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-30T03:21:41.000Z","msg":"如果靠幾條友去美國up幾句就可以左右國會決定，咁美國都好廢啫<br />\nbtw 黃之峰唔係負責喺香港同美國<br />\n匯報嘅咩？"},{"pid":"a7fd0bc6ddc246a8c013f0d78d433c77604577cf","tid":1517564,"uid":47311,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-30T03:22:22.000Z","msg":"IP 都唔駛 CHECK <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2eeb27f390b6ec0aed7c571b9f5a24340b8f55e2","tid":1517564,"uid":71133,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-30T03:23:55.000Z","msg":"要屌三毛都<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">開不推文回覆屌呀</span></span>"},{"pid":"2c9b357da46f2be8eeafc101f42d8f2c247e2298","tid":1517564,"uid":70147,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-30T03:25:55.000Z","msg":"好撚低級<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0d0ca946a7c8c6b752ab158015699ca4749e4f1c","tid":1517564,"uid":4934,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-30T03:26:13.000Z","msg":"寫專欄就係專家？<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/mock.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/mock.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8e221d11c476c3871855ae4b3c3b691b59352868","tid":1517564,"uid":6529,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-30T03:28:03.000Z","msg":"樓上呢編o野好有問題，大家唔好推<br />\n不篤灰，不割蓆"},{"pid":"2c24a6b8ec6db8771387f5aa5a0df4ab00e6d6ff","