=\"/assets/faces/pig/mock.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/mock.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-30T03:31:51.000Z","msg":"專欄作家<br />\n簡稱專家<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5c8a7b121036215d724d7903b37f0ed54503e0c8","tid":1517564,"uid":271434,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"37d17aad3b343c847c87f84d2a8a67f80661f3b1","tid":1517564,"uid":237425,"like":9,"dislike":3,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-30T03:11:02.000Z","msg":"收聲啦死廢老<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/argue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-30T03:31:59.000Z","msg":"楊衛隆已為香港問題不停奔走<br />\n<br />\n//香港茶檔成立過程<br />\n反送中運動剛剛開始，楊某全力尋求花旗茶友支持。可惜加州茶黨解散多時，電郵沒回覆，電話接不上。示威慘遭鎮壓，多位義士犧牲之後，楊某急起來不停去三藩市州政府大樓飯堂，期望踫到從東岸來探班的茶友。我住的地方距離三藩市個多小時車程，一次來回要三小時。而且，我因為私事使用傳譯員通行証進入大樓，分分鐘坐監。結果，黃天不負有心人，去了十多次之後，踫到茶友，忍不住哭起來，將香港慘況說出來。<br />\n茶友聽後，好奇地問，香港示威和花旗茶黨有甚麼關係?<br />\n我口直心快，差點說沒有關係。茶黨是美國本土草根階層政治組織，對外面的事情相當冷漠。要是香港示威和茶黨扯不上關係，找到茶友也沒用。我只是一心找茶友幫助，急如鍋上螞蟻，沒有想過這個問題。<br />\n情急之下，我說香港政治由建制販民把持，一邊是港共，另一邊是港奸，兩邊都不是好東西，香港民主運動呆滯數十年，皆因香港沒有真正爭取民主的政黨。我在香港搞茶黨運動，成立茶客萬人的香港茶檔搞政治運動。傷亡和在囚義士之中，不少係香港茶檔成員。茶友聽後大吃一驚，港共殺傷茶友，這還了得，立即答應伸出援手，全力協助。<br />\n就是這樣，茶客萬人的香港茶檔和香港茶黨運動雄圖大計轟然起動。<br />\n茶友問，香港茶檔的茶黨運動有甚麼計劃? 詳細說出來，花旗茶友會全力支持.............。<br />\n我立即將香港茶檔千年大雄圖大計說出來，說謊一次還未夠，再次說謊，而且這個謊話比先前的更加離譜，闖了禍。//"},{"pid":"9b7c99d4009701cf6d143502fe1e07d7621243f5","tid":1517564,"uid":286374,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-30T03:32:16.000Z","msg":"who?"},{"pid":"46f309c1f9d722b1818ae5f56403e31b97e78057","tid":1517564,"uid":61280,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-30T03:32:29.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>美國經濟專家楊衛隆：<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">香港人被販民出賣了</span></span><br />\n販民不是反送中運動大台，但是，販民在美國議員面前扮大台。<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">販民和建制跑去美國和美國國會議員開「閉門會議」表示建制和販民達成協議，示威者得到滿意回應，反送中運動和平結束。今天楊某收到美國吹來的風，建制販民在閉門會議向美國議員表示販民已經達到共識，反送中示威和平結束。</span></span><br />\n今日，黃之鋒和陳浩天被捕，岑子杰遇襲。林賤企圖以大規模拘捕行動瓦解示威組織，拘捕和打擊所有示威組織知名人士，包括申請示威的攪手讓反送中示威平靜下來。<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">美國人就會相信反送中示威完結，美國人可以收工。</span><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">看吧，這幾天，美國議員全部靜下來，沒有發表支持香港反送中言論。</span></span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">販民已經淪為港共政治工具，為港共效力，替林賤消愁解困。建制販民可能已經安排日後成立假自治政治，分豬肉式撈好處。香港人被販民出賣了。</span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/yeungwailung/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fyeungwailung%2F&d=Fe1Xron1KfJbBj576sEg8t%2FmPfBwacFXLzUp2rw9Z8Q%3D&h=9ac5b035\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/yeungwailung/</a></blockquote><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>楊共狗係&quot;美國經濟專家&quot;？？？咁我係咪國際經濟專家？？？？<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></strong></span></span></span>"},{"pid":"d27a9d356cfb4237071ea5a379d6d9ca897415ac","tid":1517564,"uid":61882,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-30T03:32:33.000Z","msg":"陽萎龍<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"90a4553b1ec48c1adf3d31f96454db1d6a623a4d","tid":1517564,"uid":50457,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-30T03:33:32.000Z","msg":"on 9 垃圾post開少一個洗唔洗死？<br />\n<br />\n五毛真係蝗蟲"},{"pid":"8d52df282f8da71dc6dfc619ead5704f8ff23a6b","tid":1517564,"uid":7905,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-30T03:33:49.000Z","msg":"點撚樣 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bf39892c38fe7ed21e61842c70e2802cd35890d2","tid":1517564,"uid":140326,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-30T03:33:52.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">連登仔 ： 收到風樓主老母比狗屌</span></strong></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"68309ffc5ea02546435cc816e1ba1606c59921ab","tid":1517564,"uid":53687,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-30T03:34:00.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/09/11/233251_bffd3bcc3b798ae2900acc177cb209a1.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F09%2F11%2F233251_bffd3bcc3b798ae2900acc177cb209a1.gif&h=f0f5014a&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"5d3d85978ed23e12e2f0cb140997fcd3bf255cd8","tid":1517564,"uid":266576,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-30T03:34:35.000Z","msg":"收到風，婛子會做特首，頂頂做律政師，ann姐做政務師，而同飯民傾好晒，佢地三個既人工全部自動轉帳去不同飯民政黨作交換，所以飯民知道左後都唔出聲！<br />\n<br />\n飯民出賣左人民！<br />\n<br />\nOn9"},{"pid":"95f21fbd464bd3cb53204088b5ab59c77e2ea205","tid":1517564,"uid":125079,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-30T03:35:03.000Z","msg":"唔好推文呀屌<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"34827a25080e86a82cc2c0724680c4ee2a299017","tid":1517564,"uid":247845,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-30T03:35:21.000Z","msg":"收到風<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />「專」「家」"},{"pid":"7d5ad25a027ed75c48b023fe5d7f8d597cbaf3d2","tid":1517564,"uid":48083,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"7e05d048ae21b3796aa8162c5d72af70a4400e50","tid":1517564,"uid":271434,"like":0,"dislike":9,"score":-9,"quote":{"pid":"7e371723ebcfba66a26e3b82265a58447609c9b0","tid":1517564,"uid":34213,"like":11,"dislike":1,"score":10,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-08-30T03:10:56.000Z","msg":"Who?"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-08-30T03:15:54.000Z","msg":"楊衛隆以前在蘋果日報寫隆中對專欄。已經去咗美國，同美國茶黨有密切聯繫，熟知美國國會動向"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-30T03:35:42.000Z","msg":"佢所有經濟預測炒到9彩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n今次即日又炒<br />\n美國國會: 香港警察濫暴兼涉嫌性侵示威者, 應設立「獨立調查委員會」.  反對「緊急法」<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1517223\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1517223</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"2e31c81d8cb171460d97c07071e77396345e8235","tid":1517564,"uid":275775,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-30T03:35:48.000Z","msg":"各位有興趣可以起底模式<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />有唔少分化po<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0dd35522aafdf9d76605d0bb4554d4d7c7570b3c","tid":1517564,"uid":107405,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-30T03:36:08.000Z","msg":"當老美係中共咁on9 只識聽狗奴才既訊息咁封閉咩 <br />\n會只信泛民咁就叫平息左？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />當老美D情報收集科同傳媒廢既？<br />\n<br />\n正一傻西 9成又係支那種出文分化"},{"pid":"27b608fe89511d524ba58ff392a4bc3847e7fe43","tid":1517564,"uid":209097,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-30T03:36:13.000Z","msg":"Who？"},{"pid":"ae1ed8ce1961699a30b0d2a6f5c48c1fb3d1777f","tid":1517564,"uid":263642,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-30T03:36:31.000Z","msg":"好撚低手呀<br />\n字裡行間成陣柒味<br />\n收手啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"057318844bbca993b3fa0f94129db420334cae15","tid":1517564,"uid":210612,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-30T03:36:57.000Z","msg":"分化撚收皮 blcok7"},{"pid":"bbdc26ab865d8d175f60b0b775dfd1e91fbe4b2b","tid":1517564,"uid":